      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.longislandguide.com/visit/williston-park/"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Williston Park is bordered by Mineola, East Williston, Albertson, Herricks, and Roslyn Heights, forming a tight‑knit community on Long Island.",
